articles.title: Biden is honoring Kenya with state visit as the East African nation prepares to send police to Haiti - The Associated Press
articles.description: President Joe Biden has welcomed Kenyan President William Ruto to the White House to kick off a three-day state visit. Biden is set to designate the East African nation a major non-NATO ally as it prepares to send 1,000 police officers to Haiti as part of U.N…
